headline: Pryor Cashman Welcomes Partner David Abramowicz to its White Collar + Regulatory Enforcement Practice
summary: NEW YORK, January 06, 2026--Pryor Cashman announced today that David Abramowicz has joined the firm’s New York office as a partner in the White Collar + Regulatory Enforcement Practice.
